description:
The Marvel Chess Collection is a part-work publication from Eaglemoss. Bringing together Marvel Comics greatest heroes and villains, Each fortnight builds to make a full chess set.

Each issue come with an official hand-painted figurine and magazine, which provided a detailed history and background on the featured characters.

This set includes a basic subscription issues and also has special edition issues and premimum issues that are apart of and add to this collection on top of the basic subscription issues. Each issue contains one character from the marvel universe and talks about there back history throughout their time in the marvel universe.
name: Marvel Chess Collection
